{"tid":4732,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"男自慰3小時不間斷 認為巴士女乘客愛看","createTime":"2016-11-26T15:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T04:11:15.000Z","uid":12709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35a43a45a5582898c580a39c7f5792313112092f","tid":4732,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:22:17.000Z","msg":"美國愛荷華州一名41歲男子柯瑞(Telly Shadell Corey)日前遭到民眾舉報，說他在一個巴士站附近連續自慰3小時，隨後遭到警方逮捕。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《都市報》報導，柯瑞被控玩弄運動褲裡的「小雞」，最後還裸露生殖器並自慰，時間長達3小時。柯瑞遭警方逮捕後供稱，他認為巴士站有一名女乘客「很愛這一味」，所以當眾自慰，最後柯瑞被依公然猥褻罪移送法辦。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"89b0d989b633d425addfe1283f9562448c4a2c74","tid":4732,"uid":8349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:23:36.000Z","msg":"唔係新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877b1392c8b8655345b6eee03d6b498818086505","tid":4732,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:26:59.000Z","msg":"一定勁多前列腺液<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f2a7ae2bd06cdc68e85a80380ce4e9847b26d4","tid":4732,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"41J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77abd0dda4517dec0db3e3f08d88041c2771a8f9","tid":4732,"uid":8149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小</span></span>雞"},{"pid":"da164170e6c1813d55ffb4125b545a81f52fdc4f","tid":4732,"uid":25969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:31:56.000Z","msg":"3粒鐘會唔會損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be976b9397b08168ea9adc96bb9889e2fc4ec3b","tid":4